org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl
Interface IAeReceiveHandler

All Known Implementing Classes:
AeAbstractReceiveHandler
public interface IAeReceiveHandler

Interface for pluggable receive handlers to process receives from a partner. The methods represent the public API for the BPEL engine to interact with the handlers
